summary: I know Kaine will come back, but I really really really hope he does so soon and not in, like, 10 years (counting from the ‘95,...
body:
I know Kaine will come back, but I really really really hope he does so soon and not in, like, 10 years (counting from the ‘95, which is where the story took place, of course). 

I mean, however much I do like Ben, I also want the Clone Saga to end and a stable Peter to come back and take protagonism back, already, especially since (I recognize I might be reaching and overreacting, but bear with me) Kaine’s acceptance of Ben felt like the first step in an attempt to detach him from Peter’s story and into Ben’s, so that when he officially became the lead, Kaine would stay instead of leaving with Peter (narratively speaking, not Kaine physically going where Peter goes).
